591
00:32:37,610 --> 00:32:39,290
I love the smell of this fresh seafood.

592
00:32:39,290 --> 00:32:40,460
It's so aromatic.

593
00:32:41,050 --> 00:32:41,700
Xiang,

594
00:32:41,740 --> 00:32:43,660
