599
00:32:53,610 --> 00:32:55,570
You need the energy
to report back to San.

600
00:32:58,130 --> 00:32:59,050
We found out

601
00:32:59,264 --> 00:33:02,176
that the biggest Soul Arena in the city
is in the eastern district.

602
00:33:02,192 --> 00:33:04,016
That place is full of
all sorts of characters.

603
00:33:04,128 --> 00:33:06,784
Both land soul masters and ocean
soul masters can participate.

604
00:33:06,784 --> 00:33:08,220
Any soul master visiting Hanhai City

605
00:33:08,220 --> 00:33:09,536
