609
00:33:16,464 --> 00:33:18,020
This young lady is no ordinary person.

610
00:33:18,090 --> 00:33:19,370
She's really impressive.

611
00:33:19,420 --> 00:33:20,672
She just arrived in Hanhai City

612
00:33:20,740 --> 00:33:22,320
and already has everything figured out.

613
00:33:22,770 --> 00:33:25,020
However, ocean soul masters

614
00:33:25,130 --> 00:33:26,770
fight differently from you guys.

615
00:33:27,020 --> 00:33:29,980
Even a Great Ocean Soul Master

616
00:33:30,130 --> 00:33:31,810
can destroy

617
00:33:31,900 --> 00:33:34,500
a Grand Land Soul Master.

618
00:33:35,050 --> 00:33:36,330
So fighting them

619
00:33:36,400 --> 00:33:37,680
might not work in your favor.

620
00:33:38,180 --> 00:33:39,500
Just let it go.

621
00:33:40,370 --> 00:33:41,472
I won't hide it from you.

622
00:33:42,260 --> 00:33:44,050
If you want to understand
ocean soul masters,

623
00:33:44,810 --> 00:33:47,020
you'll need to consult me, Captain Hai.

624
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:50,090
You sure know a lot, Mr. Hai.

625
00:33:50,500 --> 00:33:51,260
After hearing you,

626
00:33:51,280 --> 00:33:53,168
