we'll attract too much attention.

628
00:33:55,504 --> 00:33:57,330
We should send a representative
to compete,

629
00:33:57,700 --> 00:33:59,980
while the rest observe and analyze.

630
00:34:01,460 --> 00:34:02,020
I'll go.

631
00:34:02,130 --> 00:34:03,330
No, let me do it.

632
00:34:03,660 --> 00:34:05,850
