stretched my muscles.

633
00:34:06,624 --> 00:34:07,770
Even if it's dangerous,

634
00:34:07,770 --> 00:34:09,210
I think Xiang is up to the task.

635
00:34:09,420 --> 00:34:09,820
Fatty,

636
00:34:10,210 --> 00:34:11,340
don't you agree?

637
00:34:12,420 --> 00:34:12,980
Yes.

638
00:34:13,250 --> 00:34:13,730
Xiang,

639
00:34:14,170 --> 00:34:15,380
